{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"beginning-a-project-with-minitage-the-initial-steps\">\n<h1>Beginning a project with minitage: The Initial Steps<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#beginning-a-project-with-minitage-the-initial-steps\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"project-initialization\">\n<h2>Project initialization<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#project-initialization\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><p class=\"first\">Choose an existing  <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../paster/#minitageprojects\"><em>minitage layout</em></a> if any suits your needs.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"first\">Create the project itself and package it to be &#8216;minitage compliant&#8217;\n(uploading, versionining). To quickstart, just just an existing minitage template.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"first\">Create or edit a minibuild, in a minilays  which points to this layout:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python\"><pre>mkdir -p $mt/minilays/mynewminilay\nvim  $mt/minilays/mynewminilay/project</pre>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"first\">Maybe, it is a good time to version the minilay.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"first\">Lets go for the minimerge dance:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python\"><pre>minimerge myproject</pre>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"project-versionning\">\n<span id=\"versioning-project\"></span><h2>Project versionning<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#project-versionning\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><p class=\"first\">Play around and when your are ready, just version in this way:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li>$mt/category/project      -&gt; <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://url/buildouts/$category/myproject\">http://url/buildouts/$category/myproject</a></li>\n<li>$mt/minilays/yourproject  -&gt; <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://url/minilays/myproject\">http://url/minilays/myproject</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"first\">Don&#8217;t forget to adapt the <cite>src_uri</cite> or your minibuild:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python\"><pre>[minibuild]\n...\nsrc_uri=http://url/buildouts/$category/myproject\n...</pre>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "Beginning a project with minitage: The Initial Steps", "sourcename": "usecases/begin_project.txt", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "usecases/begin_project", "next": {"link": "../maintain_project/", "title": "Porting an exising buildout based project to be a good minitage citizen"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["usecases/maintain_project", "Porting an exising buildout based project to be a good minitage citizen", "N", "next"], ["usecases/using_minimerge", "The minitage swiss knife, <strong>minimerge</strong>", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../", "title": "Minitage in the daily use of a developer"}], "sidebars": ["searchbox.html", "globaltoc.html"], "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Beginning a project with minitage: The Initial Steps</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#project-initialization\">Project initialization</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#project-versionning\">Project versionning</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../using_minimerge/", "title": "The minitage swiss knife, <strong>minimerge</strong>"}, "metatags": ""}